Embrace your exceptional personality with @bonparfumer_id, a traditional perfumery who dedicated on developing each scent in a Paris studio using exceptional ingredients. It prides itself as an arty and chaotic perfumery where everyone is able to test, mix, compose, or collect their fragrances with total freedom. Bon Parfumeur’s universe is a clean, inclusive fragrance, and ethically made in France with a top-notch perfumer. Our expressive approach also adds a flourish of creativity to help you find your signature scent. Now its available in Indonesia, visit their pop up store at Grand Indonesia West mall floor LG until July 17th 2022 ✨
